<STR id="ZITEM_NAME_520063">Travia Cryinghawks Wig (Men)</STR>
<STR id="ZITEM_DESC_520063">Men’s wig for Travia Crayinghawks, a mercenary clan. The members of this clan value honor and social justice, and are admired by other mercenaries.</STR>

<STR id="ZITEM_NAME_520064">Axium Soulreaper Wig (Men)</STR>
