<STR id="ZITEM_NAME_522045">Travia Cryinghawks Leather Gloves (Men)</STR>
<STR id="ZITEM_DESC_522045">Men’s leather gloves for Travia Crayinghawks, a mercenary clan. The members of this clan value honor and social justice, and are admired by other mercenaries.</STR>

<STR id="ZITEM_NAME_522046">Axium Soulreaper Arm Protector (Men)</STR>
<STR id="ZITEM_DESC_522046">Protetor de Braço masculino para o Ceifador Axium, o clérigo da igreja Republicana que absorve almas possuídas e cura pacientes doentes.</STR>

<STR id="ZITEM_NAME_522047">Axium High-Class Soulreaper Gloves (Men)</STR>
